tv_dramas.title: TV Dramas
tv_dramas.description: These TV dramas are slow-burning, smart, and above all else, tailor-made for marathon-viewing.

0300008496.title: Hirugao: Love Affairs in the Afternoon
0300008496.description: A sweeping and lush romantic drama series about two young women who rebel against their sexless marriages by having adulterous affairs.

0300009901.title: Lovecraft Country
0300009901.description: Atticus Freema joins his friend Letitia and his uncle George to embark on a road trip across 1950's Jim Crow America in search of his missing father.

0300004985.title: Midsomer Murders
0300004985.description: A married veteran Detective Chief Inspector and his young sergeant investigate murders in the quaint, quirky villages of England’s Midsomer County.

0300010237.title: Mrs. Columbo
0300010237.description: The wife of televisions legendary detective, working as a small-town reporter, stumbles into a crime-fighting career of her own when she overhears a prominent attorney plotting to do away with his wife.

0300008596.title: Birds of Prey
0300008596.description: After Batman leaves New Gotham City, It’s up to Barbara Gordon aka Batgirl, Helena The Huntress, and a metahuman named Dinah to save the day.

04543.title: Blood Ties
04543.description: A private investigator teams up with a 470-year-old vampire to solve Toronto’s most curious cases involving the supernatural world.

0300009179.title: Coming Out
0300009179.description: A young man wondering about his sexuality after an erotic dream gets help from a friend to realize the truth of what he can and will be.

0300007113.title: That Girl
0300007113.description: Groundbreaking TV series about an independent woman in 1960’s New York who juggles modeling and acting, along with her tragically square boyfriend.

0300005673.title: Houdini
0300005673.description: This fascinating miniseries explores the life and work of acclaimed magician Harry Houdini: from his rise to fame, to his surprising spy affiliation.

0300008407.title: Nada Es Eterno (Doblado)
0300008407.description: Fue vendida a una poderosa familia, logra escapar, otra familia la acoge por su habilidad para los negocios y el amor llega a su vida inesperadamente.

0300006230.title: Black Widows
0300006230.description: As three 30-ish couples spend a weekend by the sea, the husbands’ fishing boat explodes - which their wives planned so that they can start life over.

0300007499.title: One Step Beyond
0300007499.description: As an extension of the tradition of radio horror dramas, this program sought out and re-created real stories of the supernatural for each episode.

03656.title: Meteor
03656.description: Two massive rocks, tumbling debris older than the solar system itself, collide in space. The course has been altered and the target is Earth.

0300005940.title: Foster Sin
0300005940.description: This video series aims to raise awareness of the mistreatment of children in the foster care system and serve as a guide to improve young lives.

0300004841.title: Snowy River: The McGregor Saga
0300004841.description: Based on the eponymous poem, unresolved sexual tension taunts an influential, widowed father in 1880s Melbourne when a free-spirited friend returns.

0300010409.title: Taken
0300010409.description: While dealing with a personal tragedy that shakes his world, CIA agent Bryan Mills fights to overcome the incident and exact revenge.

0300008051.description: Regina King, Marla Gibbs, and Jackée Harry are comedy gold in this family sitcom about life in a middle-class apartment building in Washington, D.C.

0300000101.title: Royal Feast
0300000101.description: During the Ming Dynasty's Yongle era, a young girl works her way up as a palace maid in the Imperial Food Bureau while finding unexpected romance.

0300009806.title: Oh My Ghost (Subbed)
0300009806.description: A Korean dramedy series following a naive and timid young woman whose lifestyle changes after she is possessed by a lustful virgin ghost.

0300010125.title: Underground
0300010125.description: An unflinching story of plantation slaves who band together for the fight of their lives—for their families, their future, and their freedom.

0300009739.title: The Game
0300009739.description: A spin-off of Girlfriends, this dramedy series follows the lives of women who all have relationships with professional football players.

03971.title: The Mary Higgins Clark Collection
03971.description: A series of thirteen movies based on the NY Times Best-Seller Novels and stories by Mary Higgins Clark, the Queen of Suspense, one of the world's best read authors.

0300005346.title: The Son (Español)
0300005346.description: La lucha del "primer hijo de Texas" por establecerse como un poderoso ganadero y su posterior incursión en la naciente industria del petróleo.

0300009854.title: Heartland Homicide
0300009854.description: It happens when you least expect it. Heartland Homicide chronicles stories of when horrible crimes visit quaint, small-town America.

0300007583.title: I Declare War
0300007583.description: Three organized crime families duel for control, power, and money in the underbelly of Detroit where rules don’t exist and everyone is a target.

0300005160.title: The Triangle
0300005160.description: After a large number of cargo ships disappear into the Bermuda Triangle, a specialist team uncovers a truth more disturbing than mythical legend.

0300009795.title: Emergency Couple
0300009795.description: Years after bitterness and acrimony tears apart their marriage, Jin-Hee and Chang-Min find themselves working as interns at the same hospital.

0300000091.title: Rogue
0300000091.description: Undercover detective Grace Travis' involvement with the city’s most powerful and dangerous crime family causes her to pay the ultimate price.

0300007492.title: Toradora! (Dubbed)
0300007492.description: A teen who is feared because he has his father’s same intense eyes becomes uneasy pals with his crush, a short-tempered hothead who likes his friend.

0300007679.title: The Chosen
0300007679.description: Witness the life of Christ through the ordinary people who connected with him through miracles and everyday interactions that changed the world.

0300010030.title: Mama Flora's Family
0300010030.description: After being called upon to help her troubled granddaughter, a Southern black woman in her 70s looks back on a life filled with joy and heartbreak.

04430.title: Haven
04430.description: Crime series with supernatural shadings as an FBI agent assigned to a case in Maine finds herself on the trail of unexplained and spooky occurrences.

02254.title: Cold Squad
02254.description: A police drama focusing on 'cold cases' that have gone for years without a solution, brought out of the woodwork to solve, which may date back five to fifty years.

0300006840.title: Mi Gorda Bella
0300006840.description: Valentina intentó llenar el vacío que le dejaron sus tragedias familiares comiendo dulces en exceso, pero es una joven digna de mucho amor.

0300006947.title: Highway to Heaven
0300006947.description: In this compelling drama-fantasy, a probationary angel joins a former police officer to help people with their dilemmas and challenges.

0300006547.title: The Clinic
0300006547.description: The private and professional lives of a team of doctors, nurses and other medical practitioners and staff unfold day-to-day in a busy Dublin clinic.

04604.title: The Titanic
04604.description: Follow stories of romance and adventure as passengers settle aboard the doomed ship, brought to life in this dramatic and intense miniseries.

0300006419.title: Sea Patrol
0300006419.description: Witness the thrilling and dangerous adventures of a tight-knit patrol boat crew traveling on the northern sea border of Australia.

0300007111.title: Blood on the Streets
0300007111.description:
Blood On The Streets:
An epic street drama that takes place in the gritty streets of Brooklyn New York. The battle for street supremacy extends from the Marcy projects

03678.title: Category 7: The End of the World
03678.description: To stop a civilization-ending superstorm, a courageous professor and FEMA chief must venture into the dark heart of the swirling chaos.

04004.title: A Matter of Justice
04004.description: The true story of a young Marine’s mother portrays her war against the daughter-in-law whom she suspects murdered her son, and her fight for justice.

0300009826.title: Cheese in the Trap
0300009826.description: In this drama based on a popular webtoon, a working class college girl embarks on a relationship with a sociopath who feels love for the first time.

0300000197.title: A Woman of Independent Means
0300000197.description: Follows seven decades of love, loss and courage in the life of a member of Dallas’ high society through her two marriages, three children and beyond.

0300006953.title: Boys Over Flowers
0300006953.description: In this K-Drama classic, a poor girl attends an elite school, and is bullied by the leader of F4 (the four richest boys). He falls for her - however, she has a crush on his best friend. Whom will she choose?

0203.title: Wild at Heart
0203.description: A British veterinarian and his family relocate to the African Heartland to take on the challenges of running a wild game reserve.

0300008052.title: What's Happening!!
0300008052.description: Classic ‘70s series about L.A. high school journalist Raj and his best friends Rerun and Dwayne whose antics are never unseen by his nosy sister Dee.

0300000080.title: The Book of Negroes
0300000080.description: Kidnapped in Africa and enslaved in South Carolina as a girl, a woman attempts to secure her freedom in eighteenth century North America.

0300010082.title: Third Watch
0300010082.description: A drama about the brave and dedicated people who serve as paramedics, firefighters, and police on the “third watch,” the 3:00 PM to 11:00 PM shift.

0300009966.title: The Twilight Zone
0300009966.description: In this revival of the classic anthology series, host Forest Whitaker leads us on a mysterious journey into the deepest recesses of the human psyche.

0300005549.title: Corazón Traicionado
0300005549.description: Lorena descubre que su marido es un sicario, él secuestra a su hijo para obligarla a trabajar en la casa del abogado que quiere matar.

0300009435.title: Los Caballeros Las Prefieren Brutas
0300009435.description: Un drama que trata sobre las relaciones modernas entre hombres y mujeres latinoamericanos y aborda temas como por qué la gente se casa y el machismo.

0300010076.title: Eight Is Enough
0300010076.description: This touching series follows a close-knit family as they face the hardships and challenges of the ups and downs of everyday life in a family of ten.

0300008260.title: Case Closed (Dubbed)
0300008260.description: A high school detective is attacked by two mysterious men who force him to eat a pill that causes him to transform into a 7-year-old.

0300008426.title: King
0300008426.description: After she is brought on as the lead detective of a major crime task force, a woman tackles leading a series of complicated investigations.

02166.title: Merlin
02166.description: The young wizard Merlin must keep his talent hidden in a kingdom where magic is banned as he and the future King Arthur face their destinies.

0300009902.title: Southland
0300009902.description: When a seasoned cop is assigned to train a rookie, his no-nonsense approach makes the young man question if he has what it takes to become an officer.

0300009527.title: La Heredera Gitana (Doblado)
0300009527.description: Luz fue abandonada en un río por su madrastra cuando era un bebé, y fue encontrada por una pareja de gitanos que la adoptaron.

0300005421.title: Tales of Wells Fargo
0300005421.description: For years, Jim Hardie has been a brave agent of Wells Fargo, always on the lookout for bad guys. Now, he just wants a quiet ranch life.

0300006058.title: The Client List
0300006058.description: Jennifer Love Hewitt stars as Riley, a newly single mother who accepts employment at a day spa which offers some scandalous services.

03968.title: Secrets & Lies
03968.description: A suburban family man goes on a mission to clear his name after finding the body of a four-year-old boy and becoming the chief suspect in his murder.

0300009053.title: Alfred Hitchcock Presents
0300009053.description: This series of unrelated short stories covers people of different backgrounds committing murders, thefts, and crimes caused by particular motivations.

0300007912.title: Con Olor a Fresas (Doblado)
0300007912.description: El mujeriego pobre de familia rica que le hizo perder su trabajo a Asli tendrá la oportunidad de enmendar sus errores tras su fortuito reencuentro.

0300009077.title: The Temptations
0300009077.description: This touching miniseries brings to life the true story behind the legendary Motown musical sensation of the 60s, the r&b vocal group the Temptations.

0300005636.title: The Fall
0300005636.description: The acclaimed crime series about a grim and gripping battle of wits between a brazen serial killer and a top-notch detective out to stop him.

0300000087.title: Deputy
0300000087.description: When an elected sheriff dies, an arcane rule in the county charter, forged back in the Wild West, suddenly thrusts the most unlikely man into the job.

02172.title: Satisfaction
02172.description: Satisfaction reveals the world of six high-class escorts and their manager as they juggle their private lives with their secret profession.

0300006035.title: Generation War
0300006035.description: Five young German friends are forced to navigate the everyday realities and the unconscionable moral compromises of life under Hitler's reign.

0300007921.title: Autopista al Cielo (Doblado)
0300007921.description: Un ángel enviado a la Tierra hace mancuerna con un ex policía para llevar a cabo sus misiones de ayudar a gente en distintas poblaciones.

0300007924.title: The Great Train Robbery
0300007924.description: A period crime drama based on a true criminal case, told from the side of the robbers and the other version from the investigators’ point-of-view.

04893.title: McGraw Avenue
04893.description: In a notorious Detroit neighborhood, two men with different goals navigate the streets and deal with complex characters, to both survive and dominate.

0300007076.title: Family
0300007076.description: Excellent dramatic series which follows the travails of a middle-class Californian family.

0300008169.title: Dragnet
0300008169.description: This iconic crime drama centers on Sgt. Joe Friday and his partners, as they carefully investigate a series of crimes throughout Los Angeles.

0300007894.title: Iffet (Doblado)
0300007894.description: Iffet soñaba con ser la esposa del taxista Cemil, él se casa con otra y, cuando ella se consigue un marido rico, Cemil hará todo por reconquistarla.

04532.title: Chicken Girls
04532.description: Rhyme and her friends—known by their 'ship name, "The Chicken Girls"—have been dancing together forever. But this year, everything's changing...

0300009208.title: And Never Let Her Go
0300009208.description: In this miniseries based on a true story, a passionate affair between a government aide and an attorney evolves into a dangerous obsession and murder.

0300000121.title: Hawthorne
0300000121.description: A recently-widowed nursing director and mother struggles to hold the middle ground between bureaucratic administrators and apathetic colleagues.

0300009246.title: Line of Duty
0300009246.description: Under the supervision of Superintendent Ted Hastings, British detectives in anti-corruption police unit AC-12 investigate suspected dirty cops.

02383.title: Mutant X
02383.description: A genetic engineer goes on the run with his four created mutants while seeking their own kind while a shady government operative tracks them down.

0300010244.title: Miami Vice
0300010244.description: From executive producer Michael Mann comes the explosive, groundbreaking detective show that redefined the word "cool” in the mid-1980s.

0300010053.title: Fantasy Island (2021 Series)
0300010053.description: This modern drama series takes place at a luxury resort, where any fantasy requested by guests is fulfilled—although they rarely turn out as expected.

0300009219.title: Quantico
0300009219.description: FBI recruits form friendships while training at Quantico Base. But relationships are tested when one of them becomes a suspect in a terrorist attack.

0300008259.title: The Little Rascals Best of Our Gang (In Color)
0300008259.description: Join Spanky, Alfalfa, Buckwheat, Stymie, and Porky as they pal around, going on adventures and learning about the world together.

02192.title: Andromeda
02192.description: Civilization has fallen and one ship's crew has vowed to drive back the night and rekindle the light of civilization.

0300009030.title: Suits
0300009030.description: At the top law firm in The Republic of Korea, fascinating teamwork stories revolve around the two men who are polar opposites, and yet two of a kind.

04638.title: Dark Shadows
04638.description: The classic, gothic, daytime TV series about a tormented vampire, freed from his grave after 200 years, who returns home to protect his loved ones.

0300000158.title: Hemlock Grove
0300000158.description: As a once-vibrant and now struggling community’s secrets begin to unravel, Hemlock Grove forces us to ask: What is the true nature of a monster?

0300007829.title: Rose and Maloney
0300007829.description: An investigator who was demoted after an affair with her boss and an alcoholic meltdown joins with her assistant to find wrongfully cleared criminals.

03853.title: Exploding Sun
03853.description: A spaceship with passengers, including the First Lady, makes a maiden voyage to the moon, but a violent solar storm sends it hurtling toward the sun.

0300000081.title: Hell on Wheels
0300000081.description: An epic story of post-Civil War America, focusing on a Confederate soldier who sets out to exact revenge on the Union soldiers who killed his wife.

0300009738.title: Sister, Sister
0300009738.description: Identical twins, separated at birth and adopted by different families, finally meet and try to bring their two very different parents together.

0300006868.title: Fantasy Island
0300006868.description: Dreams come true, for better or worse, in a tropical paradise, where a charming, enigmatic host and his diminutive assistant guide your magical visit.

02262.title: Dance Academy
02262.description: Fifteen-year-old Tara Webster has grown up on a farm in country Australia and has dreamt of being a dancer ever since she was a little girl. When she makes it into the National Academy of Dance - the best school in the country - she is sure her life is about to be spectacular. What Tara doesn't realise is how far behind she is in her training, and that there's a whole lot more to surviving the Academy than just dancing...

0300009557.title: El Mariachi
0300009557.description: A través de una serie de circunstancias desafortunadas, un músico de mariachi descubre que lo buscan por un asesinato que no cometió.

0300010306.title: Long Lost Family
0300010306.description: In this engaging reality series, hosts Chris Jacobs and Lisa Joyner help people reunite with long lost family members and loved ones.

0300004778.title: Heartbeat
0300004778.description: The long-running, popular series set in a small town in 1960’s England where the lives of a police department, medical staff and residents intertwine.

0300006342.title: Shameless
0300006342.description: In the Gallagher home, chaos is king, as the unconventional family runs through endless scams, affairs, and petty crimes throughout Manchester.

0300007856.title: Pure
0300007856.description: Welcome to the streets of Buffalo, New York, where a clever hustler has just robbed one of the biggest gangsters, and must now team up with an enemy.

0300008008.title: Premonición
0300008008.description: Una mujer misteriosa se despierta en el hospital. No tiene identidad y ha perdido la memoria. Sin embargo, se da cuenta que tiene poderes sobrenaturales.

0300010375.title: Invasion
0300010375.description: In this suspenseful tale, a blended family finds themselves at the center of a conspiracy designed to mask a massive alien takeover.

0300006628.title: Hart to Hart
0300006628.description: Wealthy, amorous, stylish supersleuths Jonathan and Jennifer Hart, roam the world, hobnob with the rich and famous, and solve crimes along the way

0300006557.title: No Easy Days
0300006557.description: After the U.S. President’s daughter is kidnapped, he'll have to enlist a rebellious Navy SEAL—and face his own shortcomings—to get her back.

0300008453.title: Bret Maverick
0300008453.description: James Garner returns to his original role of the slick pro poker player Bret Maverick as he settles into high adventure in the town of Sweetwater.

04091.title: La Promesa
04091.description: Son jóvenes, hermosas y presas fáciles de una red de gente sin escrúpulos que prometen una vida soñada y solo trafica con mercancía humana.

0300006728.title: Columbo
0300006728.description: This beloved series features the brilliant bumbling detective who despite his easygoing nature, always manages to crack the case.

04311.title: Loving Till It Hurts
04311.description: A six-part tale portraying the lonely, sad, yet dutiful wife of a neglectful husband, who bumps into an old flame and opens a Pandora’s box of emotions.

0300007906.title: The Fix
0300007906.description: Long after she spectacularly failed to get a conviction of a celebrity-turned-murderer, a lawyer returns 8 years later when he allegedly kills again.

0300007853.title: Estrambótica Anastasia
0300007853.description: La belleza y extravagante personalidad de una mujer de origen humilde saca de la quiebra a una conocida empresa de joyería con su trabajo como modelo.

0300000013.title: The Wolf
0300000013.description: Chu Yeown, a young man raised by wolves, falls in love with Ma Zhaixing, a general's daughter, who shares his compassion and sense of justice.

0300008705.title: Arctic Air
0300008705.description: This is a TV series about an extended family's unconventional relationships and intrigue as they run their airline in Yellowknife, Canada.

01546.title: Wolfblood
01546.description: Being a teen is hard but being a Wolfblood is even more complicated as Maddy and the others try to keep their shape-shifting secret from the world.

0300005053.title: Wycliffe
0300005053.description: In a coastal English town, an exacting detective picks through clues while investigating a wide variety of crimes in his otherwise quiet community.

0300007338.title: Mi Prima Ciela
0300007338.description: Tres primas adolescentes que viven juntas aprenden lo que es el amor condicional y cómo vivir cada día cuando tienes los días contados.

0300007403.title: The Border
0300007403.description: In a post-9/11 world of terrorism, drug trafficking, and abducted children, the elite task force of Immigration and Customs Security holds the line.

0300004932.title: Gone in the Night
0300004932.description: After their daughter is kidnapped and murdered, a grief-stricken couple is accused of the vicious crime.

0300008079.title: The Bernie Mac Show
0300008079.description: Bernie Mac stars as a stand up comic who, alongside his businesswoman wife, must take in his sister's three kids while she's in rehab.

04070.title: Renegade
04070.description: Framed for the murder of his girlfriend by his corrupt lieutenant, a renegade cop escapes the law and teams up with a pair of bounty hunters. Now he is a man on the run — for his life, freedom and revenge.

04163.title: Queens: The Virgin and the Martyr
04163.description: This opulent costume drama recounts one of the greatest political rivalries of all time. Two 16th Century Queens, Mary Stuart of Scotland and Elizabeth I of England, wage an intensely personal struggle for political and religious supremacy. The battleground is strewn with victims of murder, betrayal, and kidnapping. Lovers fall, Empires teeter, while Kings and Popes vie for the soul of England.

03615.title: CAT. 8
03615.description: The fate of all humankind is in the hands of a stubborn scientist whose warnings about an apocalyptic climate event have been too long ignored.

0300005683.title: Toda Una Dama
0300005683.description: La vida de Valeria está plagada de adversidades y malas decisiones, tanto que acaba purgando una larga condena por un delito menor.

0300009436.title: Metastasis
0300009436.description: Un remake de la serie Breaking Bad. Tras ser diagnosticado de cáncer, Walter Blanco se une con José Miguel Rosas para fabricar y vender metanfetamina.

0300008430.title: How the West Was Won
0300008430.description: A Virginia-based family leaves their home to bravely travel across the country and make a new life in the wild, untamed American West.

0300009543.title: Maria Magdalena
0300009543.description: Un melodrama bio-épico que recrea la vida de una mujer apasionada. María Magdalena, una mujer adelantada a su tiempo, feminista y pionera.

0300010071.title: Babylon 5
0300010071.description: 2258 CE. The lone space station Babylon 5 stands as the last and best hope for peace between a hundred worlds, alien and human alike.

04037.title: The American West
04037.description: Robert Redford’s documentary series about the growth of the West in the U.S. from 1865 to 1890, including the true stories behind historic legends.

04064.title: Hunter
04064.description: Renegade cop Rick Hunter partners up with the equally tough-minded Sgt. McCall to crack down on Los Angeles criminals in this gutsy '80s cop drama.

0300008571.title: The Player
0300008571.description: An ex-Fed-turned-security expert is recruited by a mysterious Vegas pit boss to prevent crimes while the rich place bets on his chances of success.

01077.title: Wildfire
01077.description: Fresh out of juvenile hall, Kris gets a chance at responsibility with a job on a struggling family ranch but soon gets caught up in complicated drama.

0300009323.title: El Sexo Débil
0300009323.description: Abandonados repentinamente por todas las mujeres de su vida, un padre y sus hijos intentan averiguar qué ha fallado. ¿Ellos pueden vivir sin ellas?

03837.title: Flood
03837.description: When rising waters threaten the lives of millions in London, marine engineers race against the clock to save the city from total devastation.

0300006821.title: Ambitions
0300006821.description: Two top Atlanta lawyers compete in personal and professional endeavors, in a battle of ambitions that so often gets out of control.

0300010472.title: A Woman Named Jackie
0300010472.description: A biographical series about Jackie Kennedy, spanning her life through the presidency of John F. Kennedy and her later marriage to Aristotle Onassis.

04753.title: Beowulf: Return to the Shieldlands
04753.description: In a world of danger populated by both humans and fantastical creatures, Beowulf must slowly reconnect with the notion of family and home.

0300009196.title: Nadie Me Dirá Como Quererte
0300009196.description: María Eugenia, una venezolana criada en París con libre pensamiento, regresa a su pais natal, donde el destino la hará sufrir muchos cambios.

0300010009.title: Calle Luna Calle Sol
0300010009.description: Una joven llena de ilusiones es víctima de un doloroso suceso que marcará su vida, aun cuando encuentre el verdadero amor tiempo después.

03697.title: V
03697.description: When human-looking aliens known as Visitors appear in every major city U.S. promoting peace, an FBI counter-terrorist discovers their deadly plot.

0300004686.title: Hermanitas Calle
0300004686.description: Se conviertieron en las grandes exponentes de la música carrillera de Colombia, dándolo todo por su familia y su carrera artística, pero a un costo.

0300008190.title: Dark Side of the Ring
0300008190.description: The acclaimed docuseries that takes on the dark history and struggles of some of world wrestling’s most notorious fighters and their private ordeals.

0300006869.title: Fantasy Island (1998 Series)
0300006869.description: The darker reboot of the popular series features more intricate stories of visitors to the magical island, who seek resolution to ethical problems.

03505.title: Jesus of Nazareth
03505.description: Acclaimed director Franco Zeffirelli and an all-star cast come together to deliver a powerful adaptation of the Gospels in 1977's Jesus Of Nazareth. From the Nativity to the Crucifixion and Resurrection, the life of Jesus is presented with stunning depth, gravity, and emotion.

0300007917.title: Secrets and Lies
0300007917.description: Juliette Lewis stars as a determined and brilliant detective whose latest murder case challenges her and her team with a family’s secrets and lies.

04733.title: La Mujer De Judas
04733.description: Una estudiante llega a la Carora con el fin de desarrollar su tesis. Ella se interesa por una ex convicta que asesinó a un sacerdote, pero muchos misterios saldrán a luz.

0300005119.title: Story of Yanxi Palace
0300005119.description: Epic drama series centered on the Qian Long dynasty in China and a young woman who poses as a palace maid to find out the truth of her sister’s death.

061.title: Lip Service
061.description: Lives, loves and lusts of Lipstick Lesbians in Scotland.

0300000159.title: Hannibal
0300000159.description: An FBI investigator with the ability to empathize with psychopaths is assigned to work with renowned psychiatrist—and secret cannibal—Hannibal Lecter.

02311.title: The Saddle Club
02311.description: Amid the excitement and thrill of the horse world, growing up seems harder than ever; but together, the Saddle Club girls are ready to take on the world. From finding the courage to compete in a major horse show in front of hundreds of people, to surviving that first broken heart, the Saddle Club girls overcome seemingly insurmountable obstacles. Stevie, Lisa and Carole struggle to support one another through the inevitable joys and sorrows associated with becoming teenagers.

0300009178.title: The Dirty D
0300009178.description: In Detroit's hottest nightclub, there are no rules, nothing is off-limits, and everyone plays for keeps! It's a dirty game! Welcome to the Dirty D!

0189.title: Outrageous Fortune
0189.description: Award winning TV series. The Wests are a one-family crime wave with a proud tradition in thievery, larceny, and petty crime - up until now.

0300006403.title: Laika en Las Estrellas
0300006403.description: Un par de adolescentes crean una agencia de detectives para intentar "salvar el mundo" rescatando animales perdidos y de esa forma salvaran su propio mundo.

0300009559.title: Farscape
0300009559.description: Thrown into a distant part of the universe, an Earth astronaut finds himself part of a fugitive alien starship crew.

037.title: City Homicide
037.description: A committed and resourceful team of homicide cops investigate action-packed murder mysteries and solve them with hard work, intuition and panache.

0300009778.title: South of Hell
0300009778.description: A supernatural thriller set in South Carolina focuses on Maria Abascal, a stunning demon-hunter-for-hire whose power stems from within.

04069.title: 21 Jump Street
04069.description: When crime escalates at an  LA high school, the police force sends four young-looking officers back to the classroom to work undercover.

0300008958.title: Bonanza
actors: Lorne Greene Pernell Roberts Dan Blocker Michael Landon Guy Williams
0300008958.description: On their 1,000-square mile Ponderosa Ranch in late-1850’s Nevada, Ben Cartwright and his three sons defend their land, business and fellow citizenry.

01939.title: The Dead Zone
01939.description: Based on characters from the Stephen King novel, a young man awakens from a coma with extraordinary psychic powers, after suffering a tragic car accident.

01076.title: 1-800-Missing
01076.description: An FBI agent devoted to finding missing people and a young psychic with visions of the lost team up to find the nation's most elusive missing persons.

0300009952.title: Moesha
0300009952.description: The everyday life of Moesha Mitchell, a vivacious young woman juggling romance, college, ever-changing family dynamics, and friendships.

0300007312.title: Sexless
0300007312.description: A group of friends, composed of two adult virgins and two celibate women, navigate maintaining their intimate relationships while abstaining from sex.

0300009020.title: The Transporter
0300009020.description: A woman, chosen to be the driver for one of the biggest drug operations in the world, must outdrive and outshoot enemies, in fabulous, exotic locales.

03254.title: The Prisoner
03254.description: After he resigns from his job, a secret agent is abducted and taken to what looks like an ideal village, except it is really a bizarre prison .

03744.title: Tin Man
03744.description: It’s a whole new yellow brick road as a mistress of evil with plans to come to Earth must face a rebellious, kind girl who sees visions in her dreams.

0337.title: McLeod's Daughters
0337.description: McLeod's Daughters tells the story of two sisters who are reunited when they inherit a vast outback cattle property in South Australia.

01501.title: Rush
01501.description: Rush is an action drama series set in a new critical incident response police unit. The members of this unit are trained to be smarter, tactically superior and technologically advantaged, mirroring the cutting edge trend in policing worldwide. It is an insider's view of police under pressure  defusing crises, saving lives and preventing crime, rather than catching the bad guys after the deed is done.

0300009830.title: Atrapada
0300009830.description: La serie gira en torno a Mariana, una joven y bella mujer que después del asesinato de sus padres se convierte en ladrona de altos vuelos.

0300009828.title: The K2
0300009828.description: A former soldier for hire known as K2 is recruited as the new bodyguard for the reclusive and illegitimate daughter of a presidential candidate.

04010.title: Cuando Vivas Conmigo
04010.description: Dos hermanas planean escapar de su tía que las maltrata desde que quedaron huérfanas. Trágicamente acaban separadas creyendo que la otra ha muerto.

0300007657.title: 800 Words
0300007657.description: A comfortable Australian journalist becomes a single father when his wife dies and soon decides to move with his two kids to New Zealand to regroup.

0300009534.title: The Real Strippers of Miami
0300009534.description: This reality series profiles some of the sexiest strippers in Miami. We show their real lives, from empowerment to supporting their dreams.

0300010181.title: Be Someone
0300010181.description: Struggling to keep his family afloat in a tough economy, a former high school football star has to make a decision that could change his life forever.

04810.title: A Woman Called Moses
04810.description: This adaptation of Marcy Heidish's novel tells the story of escaped slave Harriet Tubman who risks recapture to organize the Underground Railroad.

0300000120.title: Barney Miller
0300000120.description: This sitcom follows a New York City precinct captain and his diverse band of officers as they handle local troubles in Greenwich Village.

01496.title: Red Shoe Diaries
01496.description: Jake yearns to understand the secret life of his late fiancee. To find the answer, he solicits the most heartfelt, passionate, and intimate entries in other women's diaries. These are their stories.

0300010081.title: Nikita
0300010081.description: Betrayed by the secret government agency that made her an assassin, the charming and deadly Nikita makes it her mission to undermine the organization.

04296.title: La Selección 2: La Historia Continúa
04296.description: El relato anovelado de cinco futbolistas colombianos que por su tenacidad, sacrificio y talento se convirtieron en los héroes de todo un país.

0491.title: The Saint
0491.description: Simon Templar, a debonair Robin Hood-type character, travels around Europe trying to help people in distress while targeting the wealthy and corrupt.

0300008551.title: Sue Thomas: F.B.Eye
0300008551.description: Inspired by a true story, a deaf woman uses her lip-reading skills and trusty dog to help an FBI surveillance team bring bad guys to justice.

01502.title: Brothers in Arms
01502.description: Bikie Wars: Brothers in Arms tells the true story of two motorcycle clubs, and two men, on a journey from loyalty to rivalry with deadly consequence. On September 2nd, Fathers Day 1984, two motorcycle clubs the Bandidos and the Comancheros went to war at a public swap meet. After a brief but violent battle, seven people had been shot dead, including a young innocent bystander, and some forty other club members needed hospitalisation. Bikie Wars: Brothers in Arms is the story of how that day came to pass.

0300009078.title: A Man Called Hawk
0300009078.description: Returning to his hometown, a mysterious man for hire walks a fine line at the edge of the law as he pursues his quest to "do good for good people."

0300005055.title: Case Histories
0300005055.description: Haunted by his own violent and traumatic past, a former soldier puts his considerable skills to good use as a crusading private investigator.

03945.title: Nero: The Obscure Face of Power
03945.description: A young boy is separated from his exiled mother, lives among slaves, and is later reunited with her as they devise to make him Nero, Emperor of Rome.

0300005101.title: Doc Martin
0300005101.description: A socially awkward doctor leaves London for a scenic village in Cornwall where he cares for the locals, becomes a part of their lives, and finds love.

0300004693.title: Dark Shadows: The Beginning
0300004693.description: The Gothic ‘Dark Shadows’ world begins in this series, prior to the storyline of vampire Barnabas Collins, as a family clashes in an eerie Maine town.

0300009326.title: Señorita Pólvora
0300009326.description: La historia de una mujer bella que se enamora de un sicario. Sin embargo, descubre que su querido pertenece a uno de los cárteles más poderosos.

02181.title: Blue Heelers
02181.description: The series primarily focuses on the daily lives of Victorian police officers working at a police station in the fictional small town of Mount Thomas.

0300010209.title: Spenser: For Hire
0300010209.description: Renaissance man Spenser cruises the streets in a vintage Mustang, solving cases for those who prefer a touch of class in their private investigators.

0300009446.title: Madre (Doblado)
0300009446.description: Una maestra sustituta, se da cuenta que su estudiante está siendo abusada. Decide tomar el asunto en sus manos, pero debe vivir con las consecuencias.

0300009185.title: La Impostora (Doblado)
0300009185.description: Después de que su gemela Vitória desaparece, Verónica asume su identidad para vengarse del hombre que estafó a Vitória antes de la desaparición.

03253.title: Space 1999
03253.description: The crew of Moonbase Alpha must struggle to survive when the force from a massive explosion throws the moon out of orbit and into deep space.

0300007418.title: The Almighty Johnsons
0300007418.description: The Johnsons are four ordinary Kiwi brothers who have inherited the powers of Norse Gods. But Norse Gods lived a long time ago, and over many generations, their powers have become diluted.

0300005644.title: Rosemary's Baby
0300005644.description: Mini-series remake of the classic chiller about a couple who move to Paris only to find that their expensive apartment comes with a terrible cost.

0300009024.title: Law & Order True Crime: The Menendez Murders
0300009024.description: This gripping true-crime chapter of the franchise explores the notorious, nationally televised case of the Menendez brothers’ murder of their parents.

0300009429.title: Secrets in Plain Sight
0300009429.description: In a growing South Carolina metropolitan city, three women strive to rebuild futures destined for sabotage by their secretive, destructive pasts.

0300006767.title: Heartland
0300006767.description: Alberta sisters and their grandfather spend their years on the family ranch, where they must work through complicated issues together.

0300008356.title: Diff'rent Strokes
0300008356.description: Follows the lives of an unconventional family made up of a white millionaire widower, his daughter, and the adopted Black sons of his deceased maid.

04631.title: Degrassi: The Next Generation
04631.description: Long-running TV-series, acclaimed for its powerful realism in taking on the life-changing issues facing a group of friends at a Toronto high school.

0300005098.title: Movin' On
0300005098.description: A veteran long-haul truck driver gets into some new adventures when he mentors a young recruit as they criss-cross the highways of the United States.

0300010102.title: La Femme Nikita
0300010102.description: Condemned to death for a vicious crime she didn't commit, Nikita reluctantly chooses to live as an assassin for a secret government agency.

0300010083.title: The Tomorrow People
0300010083.description: A group of genetically advanced teens with paranormal abilities flee the agents of a paramilitary group on a mission to eradicate them.

0300008044.title: The Inbetweeners
0300008044.description: Four friends in public school enjoy their last years of shenanigans, as they prepare to face the real world in this hilarious series.

0300009900.title: Generation
0300009900.description: A group of high school students explore their identities and sexualities, challenging the antiquated social norms in their conservative community.
